headline: Baxter to Present at Barclays 27th Annual Global Healthcare Conference
summary: DEERFIELD, Ill., February 25, 2025--Baxter International Inc. (NYSE:BAX), a global medtech leader, will present at the Barclays 27th Annual Global Healthcare Conference on Wednesday, March 12, 2025. Joel Grade, Baxter’s chief financial officer, is scheduled to present at 1:00 p.m. Eastern Time.
